{"tid":2282148,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[敵人反對] 中聯辦嚴正讉責民主派議員「鬧辭」　形容是政治攬炒","createTime":"2020-11-11T15:36:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T16:06:49.000Z","uid":129513,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"13bbcf120af7c260c8bc0cc68e8170d4656d8473","tid":2282148,"uid":129513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T15:36:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559532-20201111.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559532-20201111.htm&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2AuyBzIW6ugq8wWEqYO2LRYLo%3D&h=2a6ae977\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559532-20201111.htm&h=9cffac5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559532-20201111.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n中聯辦發言人表示，嚴正讉責立法會15名民主派議員，以公民黨郭榮鏗等4人被依法認定喪失議員資格為藉口「鬧辭」，形容是對抗全國人大常委會的決定、對抗一國兩制方針，是政治攬炒，注定只是斷送自己政治前途，不會影響香港一國兩制前進的步伐。<br />\n<br />\n發言人表示，反對派議員幻想通過「鬧辭」打悲情牌，結果只會為自己製造悲劇；至於部分人妄想在國際上製造影響，博得同情和支持，注定是徒勞，少數議員違背誓言，不擁護、不效忠、肆意破壞特區憲制秩序，意圖癱瘓政府施政，勾結外力干預香港事務，已經逾越政治底線，必然被體制所拋棄。"},{"pid":"2f977f1fb14d11b1ca7aeb7c194aded0a0004a3f","tid":2282148,"uid":53922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T15:37:33.000Z","msg":"哂鳩氣。"},{"pid":"b4ad051afa75f2ac4d3886fea1ed2ed043d4ee2c","tid":2282148,"uid":68215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T15:37:55.000Z","msg":"吓 乜鳩話"},{"pid":"c50ed1e6befb19e4d10c6ff9fa5d6eed798719a6","tid":2282148,"uid":301050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T16:06:49.000Z","msg":"DQ晒佢地咪辭唔到囉柒頭"}]}